            <t:creation/>
            <t:abstract>
                <t:p>The text tells the story of St Mary's meeting with apostle Thomas and the circumstances of her enshrouding and burial.
                It displays textual affinities with the <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1640Homily">homily on Mary</t:ref> attributed to Rǝtuʿa Hāymānot.</t:p>
            </t:abstract>
